{"tid":1588870,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【賀壽行動】散步沿途景點地圖。共產C路正式出爐","createTime":"2019-09-23T04:19:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-24T03:52:14.000Z","uid":276716,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"be644ba07e771361c7bf83027876dd17e415885c","tid":1588870,"uid":276716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T04:19:33.000Z","msg":"目前港英餘孽已經將政總、中聯辦重重包圍，令愛國市民好難埋去賀壽。<br />\n但其實共產黨控制嘅黨政商機關係遍佈香港，形成一條共產C路。大家可以邊行邊賀壽，祝佢萬壽永無疆。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Yjgiivr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYjgiivr.png&h=a2bf1a51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一路以來對準黨政機關嘅行動都好少，雖然大家好關心Popo同狗鐵，但喺十月一呢個特別日子，好應該將賀壽列為主綫重點。"},{"pid":"cda0ec27aa11a2eaf209a4b1b1b94553e433a542","tid":1588870,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T04:20:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1587564\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1587564</a>"},{"pid":"229e24d0f96b15b02bdb926b7e23ae62cd26443b","tid":1588870,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T04:45:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">Brexit都係靠呢招食糊！</span><br />\n 【眾籌 Youtube 廣告】 本地文宣 : 多媒體廣告 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/dRrFcS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dRrFcS</a>"},{"pid":"8fd6fcb7ef9b1eaee7bcf8e1c8b6d7a2a8d5466f","tid":1588870,"uid":164378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T03:52:14.000Z","msg":"tuiii arrr"}]}